Package io.github.pitzzahh.atm.entity

Record Class Loan

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
io.github.pitzzahh.atm.entity.Loan
Record Components:
loanNumber - the loan number containing the current count of the loan.
accountNumber - the account number that made the loan.
dateOfLoan - the date when the loan is processed.
amount - the amount that was loan.
pending - if the loan is not yet resolved.
isDeclined - if true the loan is declined, otherwise false.
public record Loan(int loanNumber, String accountNumber, java.time.LocalDate dateOfLoan, double amount, boolean pending, boolean isDeclined) extends Record
record for loan history.
